        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081b13_29",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸法不牢固。",
        "translation": "\"All dharmas are insubstantial.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081b13_30",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "唯立在於念。",
        "translation": "They're established only in mindfulness.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081b13_31",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善解見空者。",
        "translation": "Those who well understand and see emptiness ...",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081b14_32",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一切無想念。",
        "translation": "All thoughts are nonexistent.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081b14_33",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若了一心之旨。",
        "translation": "If he understands the goal of single-mindedness.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081b14_34",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "心外自然無法可陳。",
        "translation": "There's naturally nothing outside the mind that can be explained.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081b14_35",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "豈有欣戚關懷是非干念。",
        "translation": "How could there be gladness, concern, and dry thoughts of right and wrong?'",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081b15_36",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛頌云。",
        "translation": "The Buddha's verse says.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081b15_37",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "未達境唯心。",
        "translation": "'Before realizing that the object is only mind.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081b15_38",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "起種種分別。",
        "translation": "They give rise to various kinds of discrimination.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081b16_39",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "達境唯心已。",
        "translation": "After realizing that the object is only the mind.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081b16_40",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "分別即不生。",
        "translation": "then distinctions won't arise.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081b16_41",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "既了境唯心。",
        "translation": "Having realized that the objective realm is only mind, he then discards external defining characteristics.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081b16_42",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "便捨外塵相。",
        "translation": "He then discards external defining characteristics.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081b17_43",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "從此息分別。",
        "translation": "From there, he stops discriminating.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081b17_44",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "悟平等真空。",
        "translation": "They awaken to the vacuum of equality.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081b17_45",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "故起信論云。",
        "translation": "That's why the Awakening of Faith teaches.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081b17_46",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一切境界唯心妄動。",
        "translation": "\"All objects are nothing but the mind's deluded motion.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081b18_47",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "心若不起。",
        "translation": "If the mind doesn't arise, then the characteristics of all objects cease.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081b18_48",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一切境界相滅。",
        "translation": "the characteristics of all objective realms cease.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081b18_49",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "唯一真心徧一切處。",
        "translation": "The only true mind pervades all places.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081b19_50",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故三界虗偽。",
        "translation": "Therefore, the three realms are provisional and false.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081b19_51",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "唯心所作。",
        "translation": "They are created only by the mind.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081b19_52",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "離心即無六塵境界。",
        "translation": "When we part with the mind, there are no six objects in the realm.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081b20_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "乃至一切分別。",
        "translation": "... and even all discrimination.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081b20_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "即分別自心。",
        "translation": "That's discrimination of one's own mind.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081b20_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "心不見心。",
        "translation": "The mind doesn't see the mind.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081b20_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無相可得。",
        "translation": "There are no marks to be obtained.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081b21_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "先德云。",
        "translation": "As our predecessors said.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081b21_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "心外有法。",
        "translation": "'Outside of mind there are dharmas.'",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081b21_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "生死論迴。",
        "translation": "The theory of birth-and-death turns around.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081b21_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "心外無法。",
        "translation": "There's nothing outside the mind.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081b21_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "生死永弃。",
        "translation": "birth-and-death is permanently abandoned.'",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081b22_9",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "經云。",
        "translation": "The sūtras say.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081b22_10",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸法所生唯心所現。",
        "translation": "'The only thing that arises from all dharmas is what's manifested by the mind.'",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081b22_11",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "論云。",
        "translation": "The treatise says.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081b22_12",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三界無別法。",
        "translation": "\"There are no separate dharmas in the three realms.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081b22_13",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "但是一心作。",
        "translation": "They are nothing but the work of a single mind.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081b23_14",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "既信一心。",
        "translation": "Since they believe in one mind.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081b23_15",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須以禪定冥合。",
        "translation": "It must be combined with meditation and concentration.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081b23_16",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如經云。",
        "translation": "As the sūtra says.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081b23_17",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若能教三千大千世界眾生令行十善。",
        "translation": "\"If we could teach sentient beings in a world of 3,000 great one-thousand worlds to practice the ten good qualities.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081b24_18",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不如一食頃一心靜處入一相法門。",
        "translation": "How could they not enter the Dharma entry of unity of character with one meal and one quiet place of mind?",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081b24_19",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若能諦了自心。",
        "translation": "If he could truly understand his own mind.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081c01_20",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以此定慧相應。",
        "translation": "With this concentration and wisdom combined, they'll be able to be unmoving and dusty.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081c01_21",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "則能不動塵勞。",
        "translation": "Then they can be unmoved by worldly pollution and trouble.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081c02_22",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "便成正覺。",
        "translation": "He'll then become perfectly awakened.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081c02_23",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "平生所遇。",
        "translation": "Nothing in his ordinary life has ever happened to him.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081c02_24",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "莫越於斯。",
        "translation": "Nothing is beyond this.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081c02_25",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "普動後賢。",
        "translation": "It will universally move subsequent generations of good men.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081c03_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "可書紳耳。",
        "translation": "It's written in a gentleman's ear.",
        "source": "X63n1230_001:0081c03_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    }
]